profile_positions.description:
- Trained around 300 technical personnel (Engineers and Sub-Engineers) affiliated to the National Reconstruction Authority spread over fifteen earthquake affected districts on "Seismic Retrofitting of Rural Housing in Nepal" over ten training modules;
- Building Information Modelling and Automation to efficiently handle engineering drawing demands;
- GIS Analysis and Scripting to aid project design, project monitoring and project reporting of various ongoing projects;
- Baseline surveys across wards in Thaaha Rural Municipality, Makwanpur.
